Starting tomorrow (Sunday), we're starting the Roll Call Challenge! üé∂ The Democratic National Convention was packed full of energy, inspiration and JOY! üôå <:celebrate:1252803817095958548> The innovation of doing the state/territory Roll Call to music inspired by each was definitely a highlight and we wanted to bring some of that to this group. If you didn't see the Roll Call live, check it out here - https://youtu.be/sMYMSIuxXFY?si=HTzC0TAF8HWA_xrk&t=121.

Every day between now and the election, we'll have a competition between two songs representing states/territories/etc. from the DNC Roll Call. You'll vote for your choice of songs by adding an emoji and the one with the most "votes" will go on to the next round. We'll post the songs for the day in the morning and collect all votes after 9 pm ET. Election Day will be our Championship too! üíô 

Make sure you come back every day to vote for your favorites and to see the winner. Everything will stay in this Thread so you can find it easily!
